metadata.name: Overthinking
metadata.description:
The habit of excessively analyzing, evaluating, and worrying. 

-

Maarten Léon is a collage artist from Amsterdam. He’s been collaging for over ten years, and has developed a recognition in the collage scene with his distinctive, minimalistic style. His collages are mostly inspired by introspection, relationships, and nature, and offer a reflection of how he experiences the world.

His work entails endless explorations into the miracles and absurdities of reality, often resulting in either melancholic or playful collages.
